LONG
v.
NORTH CAROLINA. No. 267P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 17, 2006. Beth Hancock, Associate Attorney General, for State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 15th day of May 2006 by Plaintiff for "Petition":
